com.github.ltennstedt.finnmath.core.linear

Class AbstractMatrix<E,V extends AbstractVector<E,V,N,B>,M extends AbstractMatrix<E,V,M,N,B>,N,B>

  • Object
    • AbstractMatrix<E,V,M,N,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of the elements of the matrix
    V - type of the related vector
    M - type of the matrix
    N - type of the maximum absolute column sum norm, maximum absolute row sum norm and the maximum norm
    B - type of the square of the norms
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigDecimalMatrix, BigIntegerMatrix, RealComplexNumberMatrix, SimpleComplexNumberMatrix

    @Beta
public abstract class AbstractMatrix<E,V extends AbstractVector<E,V,N,B>,M extends AbstractMatrix<E,V,M,N,B>,N,B>
